recommended_action:
Do not open standby DB Read-Only when Real Time Apply is active,and do not activate Real Time Apply when standby DB us opened Read-Only.  To check mode and disable Active Dataguard:
SQL> select open_mode from v$database;

OPEN_MODE
--------------------
READ ONLY WITH APPLY
If mode is "read only with apply" then perform these steps to get the standby DB back to a "mount" state:
SQL> shutdown immediate;
SQL> startup mount;
SQL> alter database recover managed standby database disconnect;
